    "description": "<p><em>Management Corporation - Strata Title Plan No. 0461</em> (Plan #0461) is a management corporation strata title (MCST) registered with Building and Construction Authority (BCA), Singapore. The form date is <em>January 1, 1970</em>.</p>\n<p>International Plaza is a 50-storey commercial cum residential mixed development situated in Tanjong Pagar.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The retail units are located from 1st to 3rd storey, office units are located on the 5th to 36th storey and 210 residential units located on the 37th to 50th storey. The covered car park facilities are also accessible from the 4th to 8th storey.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>International Plaza has achieved the “Green Mark Gold Plus” awarded by Building &amp; Construction Authority (BCA) and the “Water Efficient Building (Silver)” awarded by PUB.</p>",
